EmailTemplate.name: MX 2013 - Christmas Thank You
EmailTemplate.subject: MX Christmas 2013/2014 - Thank You
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hey Mexicans!
I just want you guys to know the significant difference you made during your Live Different Build trip. Let's quickly recap. In 10 days, you guys, with your teams built 3 homes for amazing families.You built many new relationships with our translators, volunteers, families, our staff and the people in the community! I am so amazed by your hard work and dedication to come on the trip.
All of our staff members have just returned back to the office after two weeks in Mexico for our Annual Staff Retreat. Time is really flying by this month! We were able to build two homes with our Board Members and Partners on the trip with us. It was an extremely cool opportunity to have our core Live Different members all come together in one place.
During the retreat, all of our staff members had an opportunity to share about the trips we had just been on and experienced. Heather, Andrew, Charles, Mandy, Steve and Rose could not stop talking about all the amazing people that were on the trip.
Now...down to business, here's a couple updates just in case anyone is wondering or has forgotten:
Volunteer Hours
If you need a reference letter with your 40 hours of volunteer service, please print off the attached PDF.
Reference Letters
If you need a reference letter that is specific for a scholarship, please send me an email, even if you need it 2 months from now, I would be happy to help. Otherwise, there will be someone replacing me shortly who will be able to write a reference letter as well after I leave.
Social Media
If anyone has made a video of their trip, please let me know, and I would love to post it on our Facebook page or share it with our staff.
Internship or Academy
Our internship applications for this summer is not up on the website anymore, but if anyone is interested, please email me as soon as possible.
Our academy will be starting September for our upcoming year, if you would like to find out more information, please let me know.
Don't Forget!
Share your stories, print off photos, and stay connected with the new friends you have made on the trip!
Thank You!
This is a personal thank you from each one of us staff members here at Live Different. If you did not decide to come on this trip, the lives of the people we met in Mexico wouldn't have had you to call their friend this past holiday. So from Live Different and our friends in Mexico, thanks for giving up your vacation time to help us build relationships with us.
Hope to talk to you guys again soon,
Joy Yu
